high_descs: Turn left and head to the white table
Grab the fork closest to you off the white table
Turn left and head to the counter
Place the fork in the cup that's on the counter
Grab the cup that's on the counter
Turn around and head to the white table on the right
Place the cup on the white table
anns.task_desc: Putting a cup with a fork in it on the white table

high_descs: Turn to your left and head the to white table
Pick up the fork that is sitting on the table closest to you
Turn left and walk to the counter directly in front of you
Place the fork in the gold cup
Pick up the gold cup containing the fork
Turn around and head to the white table that is on your right.
Place the gold cup on the table in front of you
anns.task_desc: Place cup containing a fork on a table

high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the fridge.
Pick up a fork from the table.
Move to the counter to the left of you and to the right of the sink.
Put the fork inside the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Move to the the table on the opposite wall of the one you picked up the fork.
Place the cup on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it on the table next to the stove.
